SOURCE: https://github.com/amzn/style-dictionary/blob/main/docs/src/content/docs/reference/Hooks/preprocessors.md#_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const myPreprocessor = {
  name: 'strip-props',
  preprocessor: async (dictionary, options) => {
    const propsToDelete = await someAPICall();

    propsToDelete.forEach((propName) => {
      delete dictionary[propName];
    });

    return dictionary;
  },
};
```

