TITLE: Defining Deprecated getPlatform Type in TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: Defines the TypeScript type signature for the deprecated `getPlatform` instance method. It takes a platform name and optional cache options, returning a Promise with detailed platform configuration (`platformConfig`) and dictionary information (`tokens`, `allTokens`, `tokenMap`). This method is superseded by `getPlatformConfig`.
